---
title: SuperQuick Creamy Butternut Squash-and-Chicken Ravioli with Balsamic, Mushrooms and Sage
description: Sweet and savoury butternut squash ravioli and pan-seared chicken are smothered in decadent balsamic-and-sage cream sauce, then topped off with earthy mushrooms for a speedy pasta dish that ticks all of the boxes.

